Incredible Thai food! This is definitely my new favorite Thai joint.  We got the tofu pad see ew, and let me tell you, it was the best I've ever had. The noodles were the perfect balance of salt and soy. The flavor was prominent but not overly saturating. The tofu was plentiful and cooked well.
